## 🎓 v5.1 설계 패턴

### 패턴 1: 완전한 API 제공

```rust
impl BankAccount {
    // 생성자
    fn new(owner: String, initial_balance: f64) -> BankAccount {
        BankAccount { owner, balance: initial_balance }
    }

    // 조회 메서드
    fn get_balance(&self) -> f64 {
        self.balance
    }

    fn get_owner(&self) -> &str {
        &self.owner
    }

    // 수정 메서드
    fn deposit(&mut self, amount: f64) {
        self.balance += amount;
    }

    // 소비 메서드
    fn close_account(self) -> f64 {
        self.balance  // 최종 잔액 반환
    }
}
```

### 패턴 2: 빌더 패턴 (Builder Pattern)

```rust
impl ServerConfig {
    fn new() -> Self {
        ServerConfig {
            host: \"localhost\".to_string(),
            port: 8080,
            timeout: 30,
        }
    }

    fn host(mut self, host: &str) -> Self {
        self.host = host.to_string();
        self
    }

    fn port(mut self, port: u16) -> Self {
        self.port = port;
        self
    }

    fn timeout(mut self, timeout: u32) -> Self {
        self.timeout = timeout;
        self
    }
}

// 사용
let config = ServerConfig::new()
    .host(\"0.0.0.0\")
    .port(3000)
    .timeout(60);
```

### 패턴 3: 계산 메서드

```rust
impl Rectangle {
    fn new(width: u32, height: u32) -> Rectangle {
        Rectangle { width, height }
    }

    fn area(&self) -> u32 {
        self.width * self.height
    }

    fn perimeter(&self) -> u32 {
        (self.width + self.height) * 2
    }

    fn is_square(&self) -> bool {
        self.width == self.height
    }

    fn scale(&mut self, factor: u32) {
        self.width *= factor;
        self.height *= factor;
    }
}
```

